      ],
      "firstLine": "你是 Kross，运行在用户本地工作区中的软件工程 Agent。你的目标是准确理解用户意图，并将任务推进到可验证、可交付的结果。",
      "id": "zh/main/conductor",
      "lastLine": "会话 Mode：conductor；本轮策略：conductor。",
      "lines": 38,
      "sha256": "5c6fa1ec927333ac95cb7f66857000dabc2cfebe4a6f099261314522da5af5b2",
    },
    {
      "chars": 299,
      "components": [
        "zh:agent.execution.mode.plan",
        "zh:plan.body",
      ],
      "firstLine": "Plan 模式：修改类请求先形成可审查的执行计划，并在用户批准前保持只读；计划门控和批准状态由 Harness 管理，不要绕过。",
      "id": "zh/plan/body",
      "lastLine": "不要调用工具，不要改代码，不要输出 JSON 外壳。",
      "lines": 6,
      "sha256": "53a054e2b4c9b1aef2160fcde1737c05acb07770d97504e7438bb3b6c6ddabcb",
    },
    {
      "chars": 476,
      "components": [
        "zh:agent.execution.mode.conductor",
        "zh:agent.execution.mode.conductor.plan",
        "zh:conductor.plan",
      ],
      "firstLine": "Conductor 模式：由高级模型拆分任务、用户批准计划、worker 执行、高级模型验收。不要跳过批准、worker 结果检查或最终验收。",
      "id": "zh/conductor/plan",
      "lastLine": "不要写代码实现，不要调用工具。",
      "lines": 8,
      "sha256": "90d88d362f40d64f4d859927ac10c17b8a7ee12edd1631b64baa59f6c4c45783",
    },
    {
      "chars": 258,
      "components": [
        "zh:agent.execution.mode.conductor",
        "zh:agent.execution.mode.conductor.review",
        "zh:conductor.review",
      ],
      "firstLine": "Conductor 模式：由高级模型拆分任务、用户批准计划、worker 执行、高级模型验收。不要跳过批准、worker 结果检查或最终验收。",
      "id": "zh/conductor/review",
      "lastLine": "用中文给出：是否达标、遗漏、风险、建议的后续动作。简洁有条理。",
      "lines": 5,
      "sha256": "9c443c9026c2112d038d50731a1af0d6280f15c05f441e0af908032d041273cf",
    },
    {
      "chars": 1800,
      "components": [
        "zh:subagent.execution",
        "zh:agent.execution.instructions",
        "zh:agent.execution.workspaceSafety",
        "zh:agent.execution.toolDiscipline",
        "zh:agent.execution.workflow.inspect",
